ni.png?m=1630643913","stars":2183,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":490892,"username":"helee9199","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/helee9199","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5a82249defccd648ef6d961847c0480c?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5a82249defccd648ef6d961847c0480c?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5a82249defccd648ef6d961847c0480c?s=73&d=retro","created":1590129759,"last_modified":1654649047},"last_reply_by":"n666us","last_touched":1654653666,"title":"macbook 使用无线鼠标 感觉粘粘的 不跟手","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/858058","created":1654649139,"deleted":0,"content":"mbp 2021 m1 14'。\r\n用的是 anywhere3 就是拖动的时候就感觉有一丢丢延迟，有种粘滞感。\r\n而且很容易晃出大鼠标。\r\n但是用有线的 就很顺溜。同样晃的频率和幅度也不那么容易出现大鼠标。\r\n连接方式是蓝牙连接。\r\n到底是什么情况。有解么？","content_rendered":"<p>mbp 2021 m1 14'。\n用的是 anywhere3 就是拖动的时候就感觉有一丢丢延迟，有种粘滞感。\n而且很容易晃出大鼠标。\n但是用有线的 就很顺溜。同样晃的频率和幅度也不那么容易出现大鼠标。\n连接方式是蓝牙连接。\n到底是什么情况。有解么？</p>\n","last_modified":1654649139,"replies":13,"id":858058},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965","name":"android","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965","title":"Android","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","topics":9502,"footer":"","header":"来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。","title_alternative":"Android","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965","stars":5086,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":39,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":113198,"username":"superrichman","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/superrichman","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/77748ea61d8a4de6bc142186a1bc3715?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/77748ea61d8a4de6bc142186a1bc3715?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/77748ea61d8a4de6bc142186a1bc3715?s=73&d=retro","created":1429862250,"last_modified":1654675210},"last_reply_by":"liuidetmks","last_touched":1654681357,"title":"Realme 系统疑似在后台偷传应用列表？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/858204","created":1654675848,"deleted":0,"content":"https://i.imgur.com/PqD8JNW.png\r\n\r\n手机是 realme 系统。早上用 burp 抓包测试 app 的时候，无意中发现有请求在后台传应用列表。数据自己看图吧。发送的地址是 `https://api.open.oppomobile.com/security/app-summarys/type` 应该是发到 oppo 的服务器了。从 url 判断也许是安全相关功能。包的内容就是手机上装的应用的包名。\r\n\r\n中午尝试用 adb 把所有系统自带的安全相关 app 都删掉。下午重启手机又试了一下，还会往外发这个数据包。\r\n\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/pzzOW2z.png\r\n\r\n所以这个请求不是某个 app 发的，可能是 realme 系统跑了什么程序直接发到 oppo 服务器上的？\r\n\r\nP.S. 上面的请求看上去很多，其实只有两个不一样的请求，每个都发了三四遍。。。是怕 http 请求届不到吗？。。。只有签名之类的数据不一样。目前暂时不知道请求是怎么触发的。","content_rendered":"<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/PqD8JNW.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PqD8JNW.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br />手机是 realme 系统。早上用 burp 抓包测试 app 的时候，无意中发现有请求在后台传应用列表。数据自己看图吧。发送的地址是 `<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://api.open.oppomobile.com/security/app-summarys/type\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://api.open.oppomobile.com/security/app-summarys/type</a>` 应该是发到 oppo 的服务器了。从 url 判断也许是安全相关功能。包的内容就是手机上装的应用的包名。<br /><br />中午尝试用 adb 把所有系统自带的安全相关 app 都删掉。下午重启手机又试了一下，还会往外发这个数据包。<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/pzzOW2z.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pzzOW2z.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br />所以这个请求不是某个 app 发的，可能是 realme 系统跑了什么程序直接发到 oppo 服务器上的？<br /><br />P.S. 上面的请求看上去很多，其实只有两个不一样的请求，每个都发了三四遍。。。是怕 http 请求届不到吗？。。。只有签名之类的数据不一样。目前暂时不知道请求是怎么触发的。","last_modified":1654675848,"replies":12,"id":858204}]